reviewText: Was disappointed in the length of the DVD.  I was looking for at least 45 min.  Also I thought the moves weren't as fun as I have done before in classes.
It works. Paid a lot for it, but it's the only one in the exhilarate package that I use. Had to buy a new one because I lost the previous one. So glad I was able to find this by itself.
